    'NG' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Revolutionizing E-commerce in Nigeria with Selldone Business OS</h2>\n\n<p>Amidst the vibrant rhythms and diverse landscapes of Nigeria, a new e-commerce narrative is emerging. Selldone Business OS, a no-plugin platform, is poised to empower Nigerian merchants to redefine their digital journey. From an array of products to a spectrum of services, subscriptions, and even files, the platform is a beacon of limitless opportunities.</p>\n\n<h3>Forge Your Digital Identity</h3>\n<p>Nigerian businesses can now amplify their online presence. With Selldone, e-commerce is seamlessly woven into your unique domain, ensuring authenticity and fostering trust with every interaction.</p>\n\n<h3>Effortless Digital Onboarding</h3>\n<p>Establishing an online storefront in Nigeria should mirror the nation's spirit of resilience and innovation. Selldone ensures a hassle-free setup, bypassing the intricacies of hosting, plugins, and templates. It's e-commerce, redefined.</p>\n\n<h3>Aligned with Nigeria's Tax Landscape</h3>\n<p>With an intrinsic understanding of Nigeria's tax regulations, Selldone offers integrated tax calculation features. This ensures businesses operate seamlessly, adhering to local taxation norms without complications.</p>\n\n<h3>For Nigeria's Ambitious Brands</h3>\n<p>From startups in Lagos to established brands in Abuja, Selldone is sculpted to scale and evolve. It's the e-commerce ally for Nigerian brands with a vision.</p>\n\n<h3>Optimized for Sales Excellence</h3>\n<p>Selldone is more than just a platform; it's a sales dynamo. Tailored for the Nigerian market, it's meticulously calibrated to convert casual browsers into loyal patrons.</p>\n\n<h3>Engaging Incentives for the Nigerian Shopper</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Discount Codes</b> to celebrate and reward shopping sprees.</li>\n    <li><b>Special Offers</b> to captivate a diverse clientele.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b> to enhance the shopping journey.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b> for those cherished moments of gifting.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing Tailored for Nigeria</h3>\n<p>Engaging the multifaceted audience of Nigeria is a breeze with Selldone's built-in auto marketing and campaigns tools. It's about crafting connections that resonate across the nation.</p>\n\n<h3>Redefining E-commerce Standards</h3>\n<p>While platforms like WooCommerce might pose challenges with hosting and offer a fragmented user experience, Selldone delivers a cohesive and intuitive journey for both merchants and shoppers.</p>\n\n<h3>Surpassing Traditional Platforms</h3>\n<p>Conventional e-commerce platforms, such as Shopify, Salesforce, or Magento, often come bundled with their set of challenges:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Information Risks</b> due to potential third-party sharing.</li>\n    <li><b>Broken Plugins</b> that can disrupt the seamless shopping flow.</li>\n    <li><b>Complex Setups</b> laden with numerous plugins and templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone simplifies this, offering Nigerian merchants a streamlined, secure, and efficient e-commerce experience.</p>\n\n<p>For the visionary merchants of Nigeria, Selldone Business OS is the future of e-commerce. Dive in and experience the evolution firsthand.</p>\n"],
