    'US' => [
        'footer_note' => "<h2>Embracing the Future of E-commerce in the United States with Selldone Business OS</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>The U.S. Merchant's Dream Platform</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In the bustling e-commerce landscape of the United States, where innovation and ambition collide, Selldone Business OS emerges as a beacon of simplicity and power. It's not just another platform; it's an experience, reminiscent of the elegance and precision that top-tier brands exude.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Features Tailored for the U.S. Merchants</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Every facet of Selldone Business OS is designed with the American merchant in mind:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li><b>Unparalleled Versatility</b>: allows merchants to sell a diverse range of products, services, subscriptions, and even files, meeting the dynamic needs of their clientele.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Brand Consistency</b>: merchants can seamlessly integrate their e-commerce store on their own domain, offering a unified brand experience.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Simplicity at its Core</b>: no more hassles of buying hosting, or juggling with plugins and templates. Everything is ready, waiting for your touch.</li>\r\n    <li><b>US Tax Compliance</b>: is a breeze with fully integrated tax calculation features, tailored specifically for the United States' intricate tax landscape.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Scalability for Ambitions</b>: ensures that whether you're a budding startup or a soaring brand, Selldone is right there, growing with you.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Optimization for Success</b>: guarantees that every element of your store is fine-tuned for sales and conversion, ensuring peak performance at all times.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Engagement Tools</b>: like discount codes, special offers, cross-sells, upsells, and gift card features keep your customers coming back for more.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Marketing Mastery</b>: is at your fingertips with built-in auto marketing tools and campaign features, ensuring your brand voice is heard far and wide.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Why Selldone Business OS Outshines the Rest</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In the vast sea of e-commerce platforms, Selldone Business OS stands as a lighthouse for merchants in the United States:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n    <li><b>Against WooCommerce</b>, which often burdens merchants with hosting costs and offers a less intuitive UI/UX, Selldone delivers a holistic, user-centric experience.</li>\r\n    <li><b>Compared to Traditional Platforms</b> like Shopify, Salesforce, and Magento, which often necessitate a plethora of plugins and templates, Selldone offers a streamlined experience. No more risks with third-party data sharing, broken plugins, or inherent complexities. Just pure, unadulterated e-commerce excellence.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>In essence, Selldone Business OS is more than just a platform. It's a vision, a commitment, and a promise to redefine the e-commerce narrative for merchants in the United States. Dive in, and experience the future of e-commerce.</p>\r\n"
