    'VN' => ['footer_note' => "<h2>Revolutionizing E-commerce in Vietnam with Selldone Business OS</h2>\n\n<p>Amidst the bustling streets and serene landscapes of Vietnam, a new e-commerce narrative is emerging. Selldone Business OS, a no-plugin platform, is setting the stage for Vietnamese merchants to elevate their digital presence. From diverse products to a wide range of services, subscriptions, and even files, the platform is a beacon of limitless opportunities.</p>\n\n<h3>Establish Your Digital Identity</h3>\n<p>For Vietnamese businesses, a strong online presence is paramount. With Selldone, e-commerce seamlessly integrates into your unique domain, ensuring authenticity and fostering a bond with every visitor.</p>\n\n<h3>Effortless Digital Transition</h3>\n<p>Initiating an online storefront in Vietnam should be as smooth as the Mekong River. Selldone ensures a hassle-free setup, bypassing the intricacies of hosting, plugins, and templates. It's e-commerce, redefined.</p>\n\n<h3>Aligned with Vietnam's Tax Landscape</h3>\n<p>With an in-depth understanding of Vietnam's tax regulations, Selldone offers integrated tax calculation features. This ensures businesses operate seamlessly, adhering to local taxation norms without any hitches.</p>\n\n<h3>For Vietnam's Ambitious Brands</h3>\n<p>From startups in Hanoi to established brands in Ho Chi Minh City, Selldone is designed to scale and evolve. It's the e-commerce partner for Vietnamese brands with a vision.</p>\n\n<h3>Optimized for Sales Excellence</h3>\n<p>Selldone is more than just a platform; it's a sales dynamo. Tailored for the Vietnamese market, it's meticulously calibrated to convert casual browsers into loyal patrons.</p>\n\n<h3>Engaging Incentives for the Vietnamese Shopper</h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><b>Discount Codes</b> to celebrate and reward shopping enthusiasts.</li>\n    <li><b>Special Offers</b> to captivate a diverse audience.</li>\n    <li><b>Cross-Sells and Upsells</b> to enhance the shopping journey.</li>\n    <li><b>Gift Card Features</b> for those cherished gifting moments.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Automated Marketing Tailored for Vietnam</h3>\n<p>Engaging the diverse audience of Vietnam is effortless with Selldone's built-in auto marketing and campaigns tools. It's about forging connections that resonate across the nation.</p>\n\n<h3>Redefining E-commerce Standards</h3>\n<p>While platforms like WooCommerce might present challenges with hosting and offer a fragmented user experience, Selldone delivers a cohesive and intuitive journey for both merchants and shoppers.</p>\n\n<h3>Surpassing Traditional Platforms</h3>\n<p>Conventional e-commerce platforms, such as Shopify, Salesforce, or Magento, often come bundled with their set of challenges:</p>\n<ol>\n    <li><b>Information Risks</b> due to potential third-party sharing.</li>\n    <li><b>Broken Plugins</b> that can disrupt the seamless shopping flow.</li>\n    <li><b>Complex Setups</b> laden with numerous plugins and templates.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Selldone simplifies this, offering Vietnamese merchants a streamlined, secure, and efficient e-commerce experience.</p>\n\n<p>For the visionary merchants of Vietnam, Selldone Business OS is the future of e-commerce. Dive in and experience the evolution firsthand.</p>\n"],
